{"word":"G1810 - ἐξαίφνης - exaíphnēs - ex-ah'-eef-nace - Suddenly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξαίφνης</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exaíphnēs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-ah'-eef-nace</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Suddenly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"சடிதியில், திடீரென்று - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"suddenly, unexpectedly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G160 - αἰφνίδιος - aiphnídios - aheef-nid'-ee-os/160\">G160</a>; <i>of</i> a <i>sudden</i> (<i>unexpectedly</i>): - suddenly. Compare <a href=\"#/G1819 - ἐξάπινα - exápina - ex-ap'-ee-nah/1819\">G1819</a>.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}